bl></cit>.<lb />2) a person extremely poor and mean: <bibl n="shak. luc 216" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 216</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. luc 216" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 216</bibl> <bibl n="shak. luc 216" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 216</bibl> <bibl n="shak. son 66.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 66, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.3.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 3, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.1.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 1, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.154" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 154</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.42" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 42</bibl> etc. etc.

